
Given I'm a registered rescurer in the GHRN and i'm on the way to service an driver who requested service
When sometihing unexpected happens interrupting my trip to the driver and I tap the "send text to driver" or "call driver"
Then the system calls the driver for me so that i can speak to them about why i may be delayed or allows me to text them about why i may be delayed

Version 2
Given I'm a registered rescurer and on the way to service a driver who requested service
When my drive is interrupted I tap the "send text to driver" or "call driver"
Then the system sends an SMS or calls the driver about why i may be delayed
